        "day": 1,
        "title": "Delhi to Agra & Agra to Delhi",
        "description": "- **07:30 AM:** Reach Hazrat Nizamuddin Station.\n\n- **08:10 AM:** Board the Gatimaan Express. Breakfast is served on board (included in the ticket).\n\n- **09:50 AM**: Arrive at Agra Cantt (AGC). You can hire a pre-paid taxi or an auto-rickshaw directly from the station.\n\n- **10:30 AM **– 01:00 PM: Explore the Taj Mahal. (Approx. 2.5 hours).\n\n- ** 01:30 PM:** Lunch at a local restaurant. Popular spots include Pinch of Spice or the Salt Cafe.\n\n- **02:30 PM **– 04:00 PM: Visit Agra Fort, a massive red sandstone UNESCO site.\n\n- **04:00 PM** – 05:00 PM: Quick stop at Itmad-ud-Daulah (Baby Taj) or sunset view from Mehtab Bagh across the river.\n\n- **05:50 PM**: Board the return Gatimaan Express. Dinner is served on board.\n\n- **07:30 PM:** Arrive back in Delhi.",
